<L>__{interior kitchen day}
<A>__{eggs cool on a plate. curtis sits at the kitchen table dressed for work. he stares vacantly at his breakfast. he looks up at hannah. she sits on the floor surrounded by toy building blocks and plays with the dog. she rubs under red's chest and in turn he licks her face. she smiles and gently pushes him away. samantha sits with her knees up drinking coffee.}
<C>__{samantha}
<D>__{curtis?}
